title: Bakery on O'Connell
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. 24-hour bakery cafe in North Adelaide. Has a vegan jam Berliner (marked VF) and a few other vegan goods such as chickpea lentil pies and cross buns, plus a chocolate glazed donut that is vegan but not labeled (ask staff). A grab n go case offers prepared salads and sandwiches (not veg).
